        <h2 id="examples">Real GBP attribute examples</h2>
        <p>Two small businesses that saw measurable lift by completing attributes.</p>

        <h3>1. Coffee shop unlocking filtered search</h3>
        <div class="url-flow">
          <span class="uf-comment"># Before: only "coffee shop" category set</span><br>
          <span class="uf-arrow">→</span> Enabled: <span class="uf-new">Free Wi-Fi, outdoor seating, wheelchair accessible</span><br>
          <span class="uf-arrow">→</span> Result: visible in "wifi cafe near me" filtered searches<br>
